**{{TO:}}** Vincent Bohart, Director, **[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-333 Site-333]**.

**{{FROM:}}** Zacharias Hanneman, Chair - Department of Zoological Studies, **[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-58 Site-58]**.

**{{SUBJECT:}}** Re:Found the back half -- Reward?
-----
Director Bohart, 

I apologize for the delay in responding to your email. As my writing predominately concerns the file you included in your message, I have attached it in my response for ease of reference: 
